{"tid":1020077,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港鐵賣唱男狂收錢 記者成功聯絡揭面紗","createTime":"2019-02-13T11:17:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-13T11:40:16.000Z","uid":166622,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"37cbaa7803be914325ab597cbc88906471231beb","tid":1020077,"uid":166622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T11:17:15.000Z","msg":"周二（12日）下午4時開始，陸續有網民上載該青年在港鐵賣唱的蹤影。他身穿紅色格仔襯衣，孭着黑色的結他袋和結他，游走於港鐵車廂內自彈自唱。結他上貼有以簡體字寫成的「為夢想加油」，旁邊附有支付寶二維碼（QR code）及其個人微信號碼。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n目擊者羅先生向東網表示，當日晚上約8時45分在港鐵黃大仙站看到該青年上車，並由車頭開始逐卡唱歌，「雖然佢冇出聲叫人畀錢，但結他袋就夾咗張10蚊，頭二卡都有兩個乘客畀咗錢佢」。羅先生遂通知港鐵石硤尾站的職員，「我故意攔佢路，佢好似知難而退咁將個結他入袋想走，但職員已經喺車外等緊佢」。<br />\n<br />\n該內地青年當時向職員解釋沒向人索款，又指自己第一天來香港，故不清楚於港鐵車廂內不能彈結他。職員向青年發出口頭警告後，便將他帶離車站範圍。記者經其微信帳號聯絡到賣唱青年，他表示自己是湖北人，今年23歲，平日工作是在酒吧駐場唱歌。當日拿了雙程證初到香港，計劃到廟街及維多利亞觀光，心情來了便在港鐵上唱歌。他又批評網上流傳的影片「音質太差」，認為「現場（唱）比視頻效果好」。<br />\n<br />\n記者其後掃描結他上的二維碼，發現連接到支付寶的付款頁面，「捐贈者」可隨意填上金額。頁面又顯示，收款人是一名叫「覃X杰」的青年，頭像顯示的照片亦與賣唱青年的樣貌相近。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Idn.dWspj05BpTTrZ4UYOQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/onccinstantnews.com/876c79297e9a76da69524c210e3527c8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FIdn.dWspj05BpTTrZ4UYOQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fonccinstantnews.com%2F876c79297e9a76da69524c210e3527c8&h=83527013&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/D_tRlE8MtYKL.PvZSmPsLg--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/onccinstantnews.com/cca7de52525479f36598f5753d705e4e\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FD_tRlE8MtYKL.PvZSmPsLg--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fonccinstantnews.com%2Fcca7de52525479f36598f5753d705e4e&h=9e55aed1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/8.JigXd2XsmSfGe1eA2WNA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/onccinstantnews.com/801554a5ec88892f858c8e92bfaab3aa\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F8.JigXd2XsmSfGe1eA2WNA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fonccinstantnews.com%2F801554a5ec88892f858c8e92bfaab3aa&h=d55f45b3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e69c168afbb1f79821db9d5078ab8cd818f96bf6","tid":1020077,"uid":2267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T11:28:09.000Z","msg":"好快坐喺大排檔有乞衣、賣唱，傷殘嚟乞錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 共享支那人榮譽"},{"pid":"b380e7a5f7de18ad3914fe0782c84e6a59305a17","tid":1020077,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T11:32:29.000Z","msg":"我叫定啲同鄉聽下佢唱歌先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71279ad1f168d753f879ebd40e7bf3bd2f60f942","tid":1020077,"uid":129469,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T11:40:16.000Z","msg":"畀得錢嘅一定都係大陸人，好地地香港點會用支那寶"}]}